There are certain minor details which when skipped, you get this exception. To solve this follow the below checklist.

1. Check if both the following dependencies are added to your `pom.xml` file. 

```lang-xml
    &lt;!-- extent reports --&gt;
    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;com.aventstack&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;extentreports&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;5.1.1&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;tech.grasshopper&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;extentreports-cucumber7-adapter&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;1.14.0&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
    &lt;!-- extent reports --&gt;
```

2. Make sure you configure your `TestRunner` with the plugin.

```lang-java

@CucumberOptions(
    features = &quot;src/test/resources/features&quot;,
    glue = &quot;org/example/step/definitions&quot;,
    plugin = { &quot;com.aventstack.extentreports.cucumber.adapter.ExtentCucumberAdapter:&quot; }
)
public class TestNGRunner extends AbstractTestNGCucumberTests {

    // to enable parallel processing override the method at runtime
    @DataProvider(parallel = true)
    @Override
    public Object[][] scenarios() {
        return super.scenarios();
    }
}

```

3. Make sure all your features files have a valid description after the `Feature` keyword. 

```lang-gherkin
# somefeature.feature file

Feature: Place the order for the product
```

4. Check all your feature files to see if you&#39;ve missed out a description for any scenario. If yes, you need to populate it.

```lang-gherkin
# somefeature.feature file

Feature: ...

  Scenario Outline: user should be able to place order and checkout items
```

So your final feature file should look similar to the below file with both step 2 and 3 completed. 

```lang-gherkin
# somefeature.feature file

Feature: Place the order for the product

  Scenario Outline: user should be able to place order and checkout items
    Given ...
    When ...
    And ...
    Then ...
    And ...
    Examples:
      | Name |
      | Tom  |
      | Cau  |
```

That&#39;s it. You should now be able to run the tests without any exception.

